    "body": "### Problem\n\n`vim.fn.simplify` seems to work inconsistently with different addresses.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1.1. macOS ❌\r\n```vim\r\n:lua =vim.fn.simplify'/Users/llaz/git/neotest-zig/lua/neotest-zig/init.lua/../../../zig/neotest-runner.zig'\r\n/Users/llaz/git/neotest-zig/lua/neotest-zig/init.lua/../../../zig/neotest-runner.zig\r\n```\r\n1.2. Windows ✅\r\n```vim\r\n:lua =vim.fn.simplify'C:/dev/git/neotest-zig/lua/neotest-zig/init.lua/../../../zig/neotest-runner.zig'\r\nC:/dev/git/neotest-zig/zig/neotest-runner.zig\r\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nPath would be simplified in both cases.\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.9.2 Build type: Release LuaJIT 2.1.0-beta3\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\n-\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacOS 13.4.1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nkitty 0.28.1\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nscreen-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nhomebrew",
